This directory contains prose templates and company-specific notes used by the operator and AI.

Files:
- `campaign-product-notes.md` — product/campaign notes for the AI
- `claude-extra.md` — additional context for the AI
- `drive-visible-note.md` — note about visible Google Drive scopes
- `operator-out-of-scope.md` — operator responsibilities considered out of scope
- `triage-answerable.md` — guidelines for answerable support questions
- `triage-domain-examples.md` — examples of domain-specific topics for triage
